    "Examples are magnetic sensors revealing open-close events (e.g., doors, cabinets, etc.",
    "), motion/presence sensors revealing movement/presence in specific areas, and smart plugs revealing the use of appliances.",
    "There is a set of target activities of interest A = {𝐴 1, 𝐴 2,..., 𝐴 𝑛 }, usually suggested by clinicians.",
    "As in most works in this domain, we consider a smart home environment inhabited by a single subject or with a sensing infrastructure able to properly associate a sensor's activation with the subject that activated it.",
    "Based on the interaction of the subject with the environment, the smart home generates a continuous stream of sensor activations and de-activations."
